@Node INTRODUCTION "STCCG.guide/Introduction"

STCCG is a card game by Decipher Inc. trying to mirror scenarios
from the well known Star Trek Universe (if you don't know the
Star Trek Universe, this document is not for you:-)

It came out first in 1994 with a @{"Basis Set" Link "XXPATH:os.guide/OS"} of 363 cards.

STCCG.guide is an AmigaGuide about this game.

See also:

        @{" Features          " Link FEATURES}
        @{" Legal information " Link LEGAL}
        @{" Requirements      " Link REQUIREMENTS}

@EndNode

