- the current @{"Glossary" link "XXPATH:glossary.guide/MAIN"} by Decipher (V 1.6)
- the current @{"Frequent Asked Questions" link "XXPATH:newfaq.guide/NEWFAQ"} by Decipher
- the Internet Series @{"Card of the day" link "XXPATH:cotd.guide/COTD"}
- the Internet Series @{"Deck of the week" link "XXPATH:dotw.guide/DOTW"}

I'll hope you enjoy this guide and the game.
